We found the Marquesa on our fourth trip to Key West and now it's the only place we stay when we go back.	We loved Key West so much, that we decided to stay another night.	We booked a three-night stay at the Marquesa last week after we had to check out of our original hotel unexpectedly.	Overall, we really enjoyed the hotel and our stay and would easily recommend it to family and friends.	We'll definitely stay at the Marquesa again on return trips to Key West.